('95809','33046','5','Newly built villa finished in a modern finca style, Monport, Porto d´Andratx'),
('95810','33047','5','Port d´Andratx is one of the most popular residential areas in Mallorca, the ideal residence for demanding property seekers. Porto d´Andratx does not only offer luxury real estate, but also a large sortiment of top restaurants, cafes, a 18 hole golf course (Camp de Mar) and a marina.\r\nThe Villa offered here sits on an approximately 2,700sqm plot in the residential area Monport. From here you have a fantastic view of the bay of Porto d´Andratx and the sea. The 930m² living space is spread over 2 floors. Over the entrance on the ground floor you enter the hall from which one you reach the living room, kitchen (Miele), utility room, guest toilet, dining room, 1 bedroom with dressing room and bathroom en suite, a separate guest apartment with living room, kitchenette, bedroom and bathroom.\r\nOn the 1st floor are the master bedroom with salon, dressing room and bathroom en suite, spa area (60m²), and 2 more bedrooms with a living room and a bathroom. A garage has space for 4 cars and a carport for 2 cars. For high-quality facilities includes furniture facility, an oil central heating (floor and radiators), air conditioning h/c, inteligent house control system, solar panels, fotofoltaik, WIFI, video surveillance and many more. Outside: it still has a large pool with 15mx5,5m counter current system, sun deck and a garden with various Palm trees, mediterranean plants and an automatic irrigation system. Top villa in a great location.\r\n'),
